{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-markdown-remark-frontmatter-slug-js","path":"/blog/masaan/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Himanshu Mishra (@OrkoHunter)","description":"Personal website and blog of Himanshu Mishra (@OrkoHunter)","author":"@OrkoHunter","siteUrl":"https://orkohunter.net"}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>तसव्वुर से उसके ही</p>\n<p>कुछ, यूँ उतर के तुम</p>\n<p>उसके नज़रों से छल करती ,</p>\n<h1 id=\"\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#\" aria-label=\" permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>.</h1>\n<p>आज छज्जे पे बैठ के उसके</p>\n<p>दिल का, अकस्मात्</p>\n<p>टोह क्यों ले रही</p>\n<h1 id=\"-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-1\" aria-label=\" 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>.</h1>\n<p>याद है वो मेले में</p>\n<p>इनायत थी मिली उसे</p>\n<p>जो गुब्बारों की सनसनी दौड़ में</p>\n<p>आतिशबाजियों के बीच</p>\n<p>मन विक्षिप्त कर दिया था तुमने</p>\n<h1 id=\"-2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-2\" aria-label=\" 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>.</h1>\n<p>जब संगम के किनारे</p>\n<p>उस शांत</p>\n<p>मदमस्त हवा के बीच</p>\n<p>सलीके में</p>\n<p>लब काँप उठे थे उसके</p>\n<h1 id=\"-3\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-3\" aria-label=\" 3 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>.</h1>\n<p>प्रेम की चरमसीमा थी वो</p>\n<p>या अमरसंगीत का शुभारम्भ</p>\n<p>जब घाट पर उस दिन</p>\n<p>तुम्हारा मोती चुरा कर उसने</p>\n<p>अपनी रूह के संग</p>\n<p>जलाया था तुम्हे</p>\n<h1 id=\"-4\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-4\" aria-label=\" 4 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>.</h1>\n<p>उन्हीं लबों से उसने</p>\n<p>सुरा उतारी थी भीतर</p>\n<p>वो दोस्त ही तो थे</p>\n<p>जो प्रेम के छाये में भी</p>\n<p>सूरज को मुट्ठी में लिए फिरते थे</p>\n<h1 id=\"-5\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-5\" aria-label=\" 5 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>.</h1>\n<p>आओ उड़ चलें फिर</p>\n<p>इस मसान से कहीं दूर</p>\n<p>लौट आएंगे जब</p>\n<p>तुम थक जाओगी</p>\n<p>अकेले गोते लगाते लगाते</p>\n<h1 id=\"-6\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-6\" aria-label=\" 6 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>.</h1>","timeToRead":1,"frontmatter":{"categories":["Non-Tech"],"date":"Nov 24, 2016","draft":false,"slug":"/blog/masaan","subtitle":"","summary":"","title":"मसान (Masaan)","image":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"70a1b8ab-18a5-5ea5-b98b-80347fd46e13","frontmatter__slug":"/blog/masaan","__params":{"frontmatter__slug":"blog"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["764694655"]}